---
title: How much do you charge for Ecgine??
category: General
number: 6
urlname: pricing 
---

Those who sings up by 31st  September 2015, will get Ecgine free for 3 months. After that we will have two pricing models: 1. Pay as you go, charged based on usage. It will cost you approximately USD 10-12 per month if you are doing around 70 transactions per month. We recommend this plan, you do not have to pay anything when you do not use the system. 2. Will be charged USD 15 per month.
